    {
      "source": "evaluator",
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I'm looking into nutritional gaps in plant-based diets. Can you explain the biological mechanism of how vitamin B12 is actually absorbed in the digestive tract, specifically the role of intrinsic factor?"
